.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-PROBE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-probe \- probe route reachability to a node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-probe
.I node_id
.I amount_msat
.SH DESCRIPTION
Uses
.B lightning-cli getroute
to check whether a route exists to
.I node_id
for the given
.IR amount_msat .
Reports hop count and estimated fee when reachable.
Returns
.B {"reachable":false}
if no route is found or the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"reachable":true,"hops":N,"fee_msat":N}
{"reachable":false}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-route-find (1),
.BR lightning-node-reachability (1)
